data.name: button113.Tag
data.value: Automatically scans the machine and attempts to remove infections. Can't be run in safe mode. Make sure you know what you are doing before using this tool. It may break your computer. See: http://www.bleepingcomputer.com/combofix/how-to-use-combofix

data.name: CacheAge.Tag
data.value: Files in cache will expire after that many days. Once a file expires, it will need to be re-downloaded. Set this box to 0 if you always want to download a fresh copy. Set it to -1 to never expire the files in chache. This may be useful if you don't happen to have internet connection.
